text: Eunidia trifuscopunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1948.BioLib.cz - Eunidia trifuscopunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1948
